STEP1
 Download arm cross toolchain for host machine
	-link	: https://releases.linaro.org/components/toolchain/binaries/7.4-2019.02/
	-folder	: arm-linux-gnueabihf 	
	-file	: gcc-linaro-7.4.1-2019.02-x86_64_arm-linux-gnueabihf.tar.xz

STEP2
 Export path of the cross-compilation toolchain
	- $ export PATH=$PATH:/path/to/bin_folder
	- $ export PATH=$PATH:/home/you2brutus/Documents/gcc-linaro-7.4.1-2019.02-x86_64_arm-linux-gnueabihf/bin
	- Append the command to ~/.bashrc : export PATH=$PATH:/home/you2brutus/Documents/gcc-linaro-7.4.1-2019.02-x86_64_arm-linux-gnueabihf/bin
	- In terminal type: $source ~/.bashrc


